  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for nvidia-open-driver-G06-signed",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for nvidia-open-driver-G06-signed fixes the following issues:\n\n- Get rid of \"'naked' return found in MITIGATION_RETHUNK build\" objtool warnings (bsc#1212841, bsc#1263834)\n- update CUDA variant to 580.159.03\n- update non-CUDA variant to 580.159.03 (bsc#1262749)\n- Fixes CVEs: CVE-2025-33221, CVE-2026-24187, CVE-2026-24182, CVE-2026-24192, CVE-2026-24194, CVE-2026-24195, CVE-2026-24196, CVE-2026-24197, CVE-2026-24198, CVE-2026-24199\n- add 'Provides: open-driver-non-cuda-variant = %version' for\n  non-CUDA variant to be able to distinguish between both variants;\n  to be used by nvidia-open-driver-G06-signed-kmp-meta for TW ... (bsc#1259740)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
